'''Adam Bareham '''(born [[July 29]], [[1950s|1953]] in Bromley, London) is an actor who played [[Jhoff/Legends|Jhoff]], a traffic control officer on the [[Executor/Legends|''Executor'']], in [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Star Wars'': Episode VI ''Return of the Jedi'']].

Bareham has appeared in a number of television shows like ''Inspector Alleyn Mysteries, Wycliffe, Minder, Doc Martin, Pie in the Sky ''and ''The Bill''.

